Vulois


Vulois arrives back at the embassy, still with a smile on his face.

"Now my mission will be easier."

But than his face grew solemn. He had been thinking about something 
he did lately, and he needed to know if it is the right thing. Vulois 
waits for Child and Windrazor to arrive.

Brix/Fliq

"Alright, come on everybody! Let's go find some computer boards."
Brix walks right past Ramulus in a great march. Being incharge of 
this mission and being on his old ship is bringing out the leader in 
Brix Prime again.

Fliq sees that Ramulus looks worse than before and just pats him on 
the back.

"Don't worry buddy. You made it and you'll be fine. Come on, let's 
go."

Fliq runs ahead to catch up with Brix.
